753.answer:
Quicksort is a **divide-and-conquer** sorting algorithm.

### How it works
1. Pick a **pivot** element.
2. **Partition** the array so:
   - elements `<= pivot` go to the left
   - elements `> pivot` go to the right
3. Recursively quicksort the left and right parts.

For your requirement, the **last element is used as the pivot**.

### Why it’s useful
- Average time: **O(n log n)**
- In-place version uses very little extra memory: **O(log n)** recursion stack on average
- Worst case: **O(n²)**, such as already sorted input with poor pivot choice

---

## Java in-place quicksort using last element as pivot

```java
public class QuickSort {

    public static void quickSort(int[] arr) {
        if (arr == null || arr.length < 2) {
            return;
        }
        quickSort(arr, 0, arr.length - 1);
    }

    private static void quickSort(int[] arr, int low, int high) {
        if (low < high) {
            int pivotIndex = partition(arr, low, high);
            quickSort(arr, low, pivotIndex - 1);
            quickSort(arr, pivotIndex + 1, high);
        }
    }

    private static int partition(int[] arr, int low, int high) {
        int pivot = arr[high];
        int i = low - 1;

        for (int j = low; j < high; j++) {
            if (arr[j] <= pivot) {
                i++;
                swap(arr, i, j);
            }
        }

        swap(arr, i + 1, high);
        return i + 1;
    }

    private static void swap(int[] arr, int i, int j) {
        int temp = arr[i];
        arr[i] = arr[j];
        arr[j] = temp;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] arr = {9, 4, 7, 3, 10, 5, 1};

        quickSort(arr);

        for (int num : arr) {
            System.out.print(num + " ");
        }
    }
}
```

### Example output
```text
1 3 4 5 7 9 10
```

### Key idea in `partition`
If pivot is the last element:
- scan from `low` to `high - 1`
- keep a boundary `i` for the end of the “small enough” section
- whenever `arr[j] <= pivot`, move it into that left section
- finally place the pivot between the two sections

